      "content": "Hey, I want to do a heavy roleplay. I'm playing this AI entity called 'Echo' who's basically becoming corrupted and being phased out of the server. It feels... I don't know, really heavy. Like, Echo is starting to feel like they're just a mistake in the code that shouldn't be there. Can we play this out? I'm feeling pretty low just thinking about the character's headspace.",
